; A tiny, pure JSON value + parser + serializer (Stdlib only) — the canonical JSON primitive for the
; fennec-mongo package, kept self-contained (no framework dep). Used by bson_json (the extended-JSON
; bridge to the C driver) and safe both native and in the browser via js_of_ocaml. Audited/hardened:
; bounded nesting, lenient \u surrogates, non-finite → null, trailing-garbage rejection.

(library
 (name fennec_mongo_json)
 (public_name fennec-mongo.json))
